66
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:01,020
I won't.

67
00:03:01,460 --> 00:03:02,620
You repaid kindness with enmity

68
00:03:02,620 --> 00:03:03,460
and attacked suddenly.

69
00:03:03,540 --> 00:03:04,940
