307
00:13:43,820 --> 00:13:44,660
I...

308
00:13:46,660 --> 00:13:47,780
Anyone else?

309
00:13:48,380 --> 00:13:49,220
Master.

310
00:13:49,380 --> 00:13:50,460
- You all...
- Master.

