327
00:15:35,900 --> 00:15:36,860
Are you the ghost?

328
00:15:37,060 --> 00:15:38,300
There really is a ghost.

329
00:15:38,300 --> 00:15:40,460
Wearing a white robe, floating

330
00:15:40,460 --> 00:15:41,900
