00:16:02,500 --> 00:16:03,460
People are coming.

338
00:16:04,340 --> 00:16:05,260
Watch closely.

339
00:16:09,300 --> 00:16:10,140
Big Feet,

340
00:16:11,100 --> 00:16:13,740
