352
00:16:40,580 --> 00:16:41,540
I'm not, I'm not.

353
00:16:43,860 --> 00:16:45,340
Caught you!

354
00:16:49,020 --> 00:16:49,860
Dr. Bai,

355
00:16:50,220 --> 00:16:51,140
