- Master!

441
00:20:39,900 --> 00:20:41,080
- Xiaolu.
- Master.

442
00:20:41,180 --> 00:20:42,100
Lu Xiaolu,

443
00:20:42,780 --> 00:20:44,100
why are you

444
00:20:44,100 --> 00:20:45,140
in every trouble?

445
00:20:47,340 --> 00:20:48,180
Director Liu,

446
00:20:48,420 --> 00:20:49,420
I came up with the idea

447
00:20:49,620 --> 00:20:50,660
